author: mullan
msg: Fixed corrupted binary cert and crl data files. Also removed the svn:eol-style
property (which was incorrectly set to native) and set the svn:mime-type
keyword to application/pkix-cert (for certs), application/pkix-crl (for crls)
and application/octet-stream (for keystores) so that svn would recognize these
as binary files and avoid the merge corruption issues which can happen if
they are treated as text files.

author: markt
msg: Use procrun from commons-daemon rather than JavaService to enable Tomcat to run as a service on Windows.

author: rickhall
msg: Modified the Felix bundle cache to support installing bundles by referenced
JAR files as well as exploded directories. These changes percolated into
various other areaas of the impl which are also changed here.
